lxd-openwrt
===========

Scripts for building LXD images from OpenWrt rootfs tar balls. The OpenWrt SDK is used to build a patched procd package.

Requirements
------------
Subversion is required in addition to the software needed to build the packages on the SDK.
(Refer to https://openwrt.org/docs/guide-developer/obtain.firmware.sdk).

Configuration
-------------
Refer to the beginning of build.sh.
